New "wifi_module" boolean config flag: a status line is emittd every seconds on the UART.

Every second, a line with [PosX PosY PosZ Speed PercentPlay Secondsplay ActiveExtruder NbExtruders ExtPos1 Extflow1... NbHeaters Temp1 Target1 PWM1... fan] is sent to the kernel serial interface which is supposed ly connected to an EST8266 module.
Change the initial MR0 value which otherwise generates a large number of initial counts.
